### CI/CD集成
```yaml
# .github/workflows/xp-coding-governance.yml
name: XPeng Coding Governance
on: [push, pull_request]

jobs:
  governance-check:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3
      - name: Setup Python
        uses: actions/setup-python@v4
        with:
          python-version: '3.11'
      - name: Run Governance Validation
        run: python tools/validate_xp_ai_coding.py --project .
```

